            "title": "North Korea says South Korea infringed on its airspace with another drone on Jan 4",
            "description": "<div class=\"txt-s4 article-text\"><p>SEOUL, Jan 10 (Reuters) - North Korea said on Saturday that South Korea sent another drone into North Korean airspace on January 4, infringing on its sovereignty, North Korean state media KCNA said. </p><p>\n              The drone, which flew from around the South Korean city of Incheon, was allowed to fly 8 kilometres before North Korea shot it down in North Korean airspace, KCNA said, citing a spokesperson for the North Korean military.  </p><!-- Article --><p></p><p> (Reporting by Joyce Lee; Editing by Chris Reese)</p></div>",
